  <entry>
    <title>Git基础</title>
    <url>/2024/08/03/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/Git/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="一-git基础"><a href="#一-git基础" class="headerlink" title="一.git基础"></a>一.git基础</h2><ol>
<li><p>初始化git仓库</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<span id="more"></span>
</li>
<li><p>添加文件</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git add readme.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>提交文件</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;submit infomation&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


</li>
<li><p>查看工作区状态</p>
</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git status</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<ol start="5">
<li>查看修改内容</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git diff</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<ol start="6">
<li>查看提交历史</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git log</span><br><span class="line">git reflog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<ol start="7">
<li>回退版本</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git reset --hard 7376(版本号)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<ol start="8">
<li>撤销暂存区的修改</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git reset HEAD readme.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<ol start="9">
<li>撤销工作区的修改</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git checkout -- readme.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<ol start="10">
<li>删除版本库的文件</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git rm readme.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<ol start="11">
<li>管理github仓库</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git remote add origin git@github.com:skyang1/learngit.git</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git remote -v   // 查看关联仓库</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<ol start="12">
<li>推送本地库的所有内容到github</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git push -u origin master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>由于远程库是空的，我们第一次推送<code>master</code>分支时，加上了<code>-u</code>参数，Git不但会把本地的<code>master</code>分支内容推送的远程新的<code>master</code>分支，还会把本地的<code>master</code>分支和远程的<code>master</code>分支关联起来，在以后的推送或者拉取时就可以简化命令。</p>
<ol start="13">
<li>克隆github项目</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone git@github.com:LeiWang1999/FPGA.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="二、分支管理"><a href="#二、分支管理" class="headerlink" title="二、分支管理"></a>二、分支管理</h2><ol>
<li>查看分支</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git branch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="2">
<li>创建分支</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git branch dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<ol start="3">
<li>切换分支</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git switch dev</span><br><span class="line">git checkout dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<ol start="4">
<li>创建并切换分支</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git switch -c dev</span><br><span class="line">git checkout -b dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<ol start="5">
<li>合并某分支到当前分支</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git merge dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<ol start="6">
<li>删除分支</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git branch -d dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
